edu.uchsc.ccp.dmap.configuration
Class ParserFactory

java.lang.Object
  edu.uchsc.ccp.dmap.configuration.ParserFactory

public class ParserFactory
extends java.lang.Object

This is a factory class for creating new parser instances. It simplifies some of the configuration of the parser using XML configuration files.

Using this class is the best way to create a new parser instance.

Author:
R. James Firby
